CFOP Scripts

CFOP is a web database application written in PHP with a MySQL backend database.
This delivery contains a subset of CFOP scripts that provide the following functionality:

- Display all the KOIs on CFOP (file #5) and link to individual page for a KOI (file #4)
- Display and edit the observing notes for a KOI (file #3)
- Display all imaging/spectroscopy observations for all KOIs (files #6 and #7)

List of files in this delivery:

1. config.php
Configuration file which contains database connection information, directory names,
commonly used arrays, etc.  

*** Please note that the PHP extension "mysql_connect" is deprecated and the newer
    extension "mysqli_connect" should be used.
    
2. coord_convert.php
Functions for converting coordinates

3. edit_obsnotes.php
Page which displays existing observing notes and provides a form for entering
new notes for an individual KOI

4. edit_target.php
Displays parameters and files for an individual KOI

5. targets.php
Lists all KOIs and displays links to individual KOI pages (file #4), 
finding charts, and observing notes (file #3)

6. view_imaging.php
Displays all imaging observations of all KOIs by all users.

7. view_spect.php
Displays all spectroscopy observations of all KOIs by all users.


